1111
00:51:08,310 --> 00:51:09,907
- [Performer] Are you Dr. Fiasco?

1112
00:51:09,990 --> 00:51:10,740
- Yes.

1113
00:51:10,823 --> 00:51:13,177
- Happy birthday, Dr. Fiasco!

1114
00:51:13,260 --> 00:51:14,343
From your staff!

1115
00:51:15,720 --> 00:51:17,072
- What's the matter?

1116
00:51:17,155 --> 00:51:19,237
(June shouts)

1117
00:51:19,320 --> 00:51:21,187
- What's wrong with you people?

1118
00:51:21,270 --> 00:51:22,195
- But what is it?

1119
00:51:22,278 --> 00:51:23,887
- It's a clown.

1120
00:51:23,970 --> 00:51:25,317
- You see them too?

1121
00:51:25,400 --> 00:51:27,363
Then I'm not crazy!

1122
00:51:31,560 --> 00:51:32,393
What clown?

1123
00:51:33,561 --> 00:51:37,057
(Playful carnival music)

1124
00:51:37,140 --> 00:51:38,437
- Your people are nuts.

1125
00:51:38,520 --> 00:51:39,663
I'm quitting this job.

1126
00:51:40,721 --> 00:51:44,304
(Carnival music continues)

1127
00:51:45,165 --> 00:51:47,748
(Chair clangs)

1128
00:51:51,410 --> 00:51:52,243
- Ah.

1129
00:51:54,279 --> 00:51:56,227
This looks like the place.

1130
00:51:56,310 --> 00:51:57,513
Let's see now.

1131
00:51:58,350 --> 00:52:02,287
Pour witch Hazel over the grave.

1132
00:52:02,370 --> 00:52:05,864
And let's see.

1133
00:52:05,947 --> 00:52:07,827
"House of seven gables."

1134
00:52:10,560 --> 00:52:13,210
Halfway down a by street
of one of our new England...

1135
00:52:14,280 --> 00:52:16,477
Oh, backwards, I read it backwards.

1136
00:52:16,560 --> 00:52:17,857
I don't wanna mess this up, let's see.

1137
00:52:17,940 --> 00:52:19,263
And fast, yes.

1138
00:52:20,130 --> 00:52:21,127
Story from the house of seven gables

1139
00:52:21,210 --> 00:52:22,297
of a spirit's joy upon her harpsichord,

1140
00:52:22,380 --> 00:52:23,268
as she floated heavenwards off to kindred.

1141
00:52:23,351 --> 00:52:25,177
(Jasper reading indistinctly)

1142
00:52:25,260 --> 00:52:26,280
Bygone it seemed the present hepzibah.

1143
00:52:26,363 --> 00:52:28,177
(Jasper reading indistinctly)

