1263
00:57:27,423 --> 00:57:29,917
Now, would you please leave my office?

1264
00:57:30,000 --> 00:57:31,939
I'm sure you're late for
your electro shock therapy.

1265
00:57:32,022 --> 00:57:34,477
(Eerie music)

1266
00:57:34,560 --> 00:57:37,169
- Your mouth spills
forth meaningless drivel.

1267
00:57:37,252 --> 00:57:39,877
I shan't leave until you
answer my question.

1268
00:57:39,960 --> 00:57:42,907
Did you not give one Jasper loon the secret

1269
00:57:42,990 --> 00:57:44,467
