1270
00:57:44,550 --> 00:57:46,612
- I know a Jasper coukos, not loon.

1271
00:57:46,695 --> 00:57:49,897
- Answer me, large-mouthed one.

1272
00:57:49,980 --> 00:57:52,614
Did you tell him the
secret of raising the dead?

1273
00:57:52,697 --> 00:57:55,517
- It was a crackpot I sold
an insurance policy too.

1274
00:57:55,600 --> 00:57:57,034
He asked me a stupid question,

1275
00:57:57,117 --> 00:57:58,597
and I gave him a stupid answer.

1276
00:57:58,680 --> 00:58:00,517
I got rid of him, no harm done.

1277
00:58:00,600 --> 00:58:04,904
