back from peaceful death.

1278
00:58:04,987 --> 00:58:09,987
I had no desire to return
to this wretched existence.

1279
00:58:10,710 --> 00:58:12,697
But now that I am here,

1280
00:58:12,780 --> 00:58:16,638
I shall complete my revenge on the loons.

1281
00:58:16,721 --> 00:58:19,554
(Energy whirring)

1282
00:58:21,575 --> 00:58:23,797
- How did you do that? - You fool.

1283
00:58:23,880 --> 00:58:26,377
My power is in my eyes.

1284
00:58:26,460 --> 00:58:29,377
What an ignorant age this is.

1285
00:58:29,460 --> 00:58:33,427
Your mouth far exceeds your intelligence.

1286
00:58:33,510 --> 00:58:35,557
I will make the two equal.

1287
00:58:35,640 --> 00:58:38,984
Your mouth will be as small as your brain.

1288
00:58:39,067 --> 00:58:41,567
(Eerie music)

1289
