(Hepzibah laughs)

1290
00:58:48,503 --> 00:58:51,003
(Energy zaps)

1291
00:58:55,103 --> 00:58:56,497
(Energy zaps)

1292
00:58:56,580 --> 00:59:00,547
So you are a loon.

1293
00:59:00,630 --> 00:59:02,841
Or should I say coukos?

1294
00:59:02,924 --> 00:59:04,037
- Who's there?

1295
00:59:04,120 --> 00:59:05,005
Why can't I move?

1296
00:59:05,088 --> 00:59:08,407
- It is I, hepzibah Crowley!

1297
00:59:08,490 --> 00:59:09,817
- The witch?

1298
00:59:09,900 --> 00:59:10,717
You're the witch that...

1299
00:59:10,800 --> 00:59:15,397
